text:
According to Hashmi et al. (2021a), on “ICDAR2013 Table Competition” dataset (Göbel et al., 2013), F1-score is close to 1.0 for TD when the threshold of
“Intersection Over Union” (IOU) equals 0.5, and this score reaches 0.95 (IOU = 0.5) for TSR.
The task statements of TD/TSR are essentially different for DTE (Zanibbi et al., 2004; Hashmi et al., 2021a), WTE (Rold an et al., 2020; Zhang and Balog, 2020), and STE (Bonfitto et al., 2021).
